{"tid":2201793,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"《社交網絡》《白宮群英》編劇Aaron Sorkin 最新作《芝加哥七人案》預告","createTime":"2020-09-14T05:37:45.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-09T15:05:25.000Z","uid":41343,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"878cb5ff3f565c93db8e1ab8215902ae3eeb9226","tid":2201793,"uid":41343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-14T05:37:45.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/gydxs5PQOwA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fgydxs5PQOwA&d=L%2FLAiDqbkajbTQHtoaAw8Mv4r%2BPR%2BKiJG6VnsQYGapQ%3D&h=1346e961\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/gydxs5PQOwA</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n《芝加哥七人案：驚世審判》由艾倫索金編劇執導，的故事背景設定在 1968 年的美國，當時民主黨在伊利諾州芝加哥召開全國代表大會，期間有七名社會運動人士因反越戰所發起的示威行動而遭到逮捕，並面臨到各式各樣的指控。<br />\n<br />\n豪華的演出卡司包括薩夏拜倫科恩（Sacha Baron Cohen）、艾迪瑞德曼（Eddie Redmayne）、米高基頓（Micheal Keaton）、馬克瑞蘭斯（Mark Rylance）、喬瑟夫高登李維（Joseph Gordon-Levitt）、葉海亞阿巴杜馬汀二世（Yahya Abdul-Mateen II）、傑瑞米史壯（Jeremy Strong）等，預計 10 月 16 日全球同步上線。"},{"pid":"c1370f82dae8cad1b9ad30c019a5e6169aec7ad4","tid":2201793,"uid":157092,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-14T13:29:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />今年Netflix 咁多正野<br />\nI'm Thinking of Ending Things <br />\nMank <br />\nPieces of a Women"},{"pid":"a91bf548a122215e6a4fd275881d3af8827a9814","tid":2201793,"uid":48631,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-14T13:32:05.000Z","msg":"近期有邊套netflix oringinal嘅戲係ok?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e6feb0f5cb7c1f78bd13cc923abe70edd156092d","tid":2201793,"uid":157092,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a91bf548a122215e6a4fd275881d3af8827a9814","tid":2201793,"uid":48631,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-14T13:32:05.000Z","msg":"近期有邊套netflix oringinal嘅戲係ok?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-14T14:53:02.000Z","msg":"<im